name: ELEFANCLUB 02
description:
A weekly original illustration for collectors of Les Elefants Terribles. 

"It’s happening, it happened, the same old crap.
We lost our mutt by the banks of our own lagoon.

Where banana slugs read modesty blaise,
not even confident which end that came out of.

Where in place of Trish’s stove, 
wolf and his gang peed on a chair.

There’s nothing worse than being ordinary.
So out damned spot and spark a five family war!

As with 78 setups and plenty of ketchup,
this IS the worst toilet on Tezos."

Rotring pen and markers on paper

By Guillaume Cornet and Only Child No Pets
Follow @elefants_tez on twitter
